<hw>Ag*gress"</hw>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To set upon; to attack.</def>
<mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Aggress</ent>⟦br⟧

